data.name: ReadCodeValue1
data.value: select top(1) COV_ID, COD_ID, CDVALUE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, EXPIRATION_DATE, DESCRIPTION from CKT_CODE_VALUE where (COD_ID = @codId) and (CDVALUE = cast(@coverageCode1 as char(2))) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (EXPIRATION_DATE > @effectiveDate)
